OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChannel 4 boss: Brand      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fallegations are horrendous 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Channel 4 CEO Alex Mahon has said the  
OL,6, allegations made against Russell Brand 
OL,7, are "horrendous" and that the industry 
OL,8, needs to confront bad behaviour.       
OL,10,FThe star has been accused of rape and  
OL,11,Fsexual assaults, which he denies.      
OL,13,FMs Mahon added that as "a woman in our 
OL,14,Findustry" she found the claims         
OL,15,F"disgusting and saddening".            
OL,17,FHer comments come a day after the BBC's
OL,18,Fdirector general announced a review of 
OL,19,Fcomplaints against Brand during his    
OL,20,Ftime working for the corporation.      
